news.title: BNP Paribas, Societe Generale trim stake in Indiabulls Housing
news.para: ​According to bulk deal data available with the NSE, Societe Generale sold 27.40 lakh shares of Indiabulls Housing Finance while BNP Paribas Arbitrage divested 23.59 lakh shares of the company.

news.title: China's Kaisa Group seeks to extend maturity on $400 million offshore bond
news.para: If at least 95% of the holders of the offshore bond accept its offer, it will exchange the 6.5% notes due Dec. 7 for new notes due June 6, 2023 at the same interest rate, it said in a company filing.

news.title: Housing market trends fuel single-family home rental growth
news.para: While individual homeowners and mom-and-pop investors still account for the vast majority of single-family rental homes, homebuilders have stepped up construction this year of new houses being built for rent.
